**Asked:** Audit `infer.ts` for `getComputedStyle` performance — verify it's cached per selection, not called on render/drag.
**Did:** Traced all 18 call sites in `Overlay.tsx` plus confirmed no child component imports `infer`. Every call is in a `useCallback`/`useEffect` (discrete events only). The spacing drag handler patches state surgically without re-inferring. No performance issue — no changes required.
